{"type":"message","id":"1d796aa1","parentId":"07bc9da9","timestamp":"2026-03-08T17:28:45.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The browser isn't available. Let me check if there are other browser options like a regular `open` command (macOS) or if there's a way to use curl/playwright.\n\nActually, I can try to log into console.anthropic.com using curl with the OAuth token, or I can just try to navigate using the native macOS `open` command to open the links in the user's default browser. But that would require user interaction.\n\nAlternatively, let me try to use curl to access the Anthropic console API with the token - the OAuth admin token might work with the console API. The console at console.anthropic.com is a web app that communicates with its backend API.\n\n\nI need to figure out what API endpoints the Anthropic console uses to fetch the data I'm looking for.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01GFwq4KwMneQCeMMimBWw31","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ANTHROPIC_TOKEN=\"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\"\n\n# Try the Anthropic admin API - these are the real endpoints for the admin/console API\n# The oat token is an \"Organization Admin Token\" used specifically with the admin API\necho \"=== Try admin API key list ===\"\ncurl -s \"https://api.anthropic.com/v1/api_keys\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-beta: admin-api-2025-05-15\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: $ANTHROPIC_TOKEN\" | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -40\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Try usage data endpoint ===\"\n# Usage endpoint format from Anthropic docs\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nSTART=\"2026-03-01\"\ncurl -s \"https://api.anthropic.com/v1/usage?start_date=${START}&end_date=${TODAY}&bucket_duration=day\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n  -H \"anthropic-beta: admin-api-2025-05-15\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: $ANTHROPIC_TOKEN\" | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":640,"cacheRead":30473,"cacheWrite":107,"totalTokens":31221,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.009600000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0091419,"cacheWrite":0.00040125,"total":0.01914615}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772990910101}}
