{"type":"message","id":"e869725a","parentId":"2eef46a9","timestamp":"2026-03-08T17:34:43.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the `sk-ant-oat01` token is stored as a `token` type (not oauth or api_key). It's a Claude OAuth token from the Claude.ai subscription, used for the API. \n\nWith a Claude OAuth subscription (Claude Pro/Team/etc.), there's no credit balance to check. The usage is:\n- Subscription-based with message limits\n- Can be checked at claude.ai/settings or claude.ai/settings/subscription\n\nSince the `claude.ai` API requires Cloudflare browser challenge to access, I can't easily scrape it via curl. The user would need to go to claude.ai manually to check their plan/usage.\n\n\nI'll provide them with direct links to those settings pages so they can check their subscription status and usage limits themselves.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Claude.ai is behind Cloudflare — won't work without a real browser session with cookies. Here's the deal:\n\n**With Claude OAuth (Pro/Team subscription):**\n- No credit balance — it's a flat subscription\n- Usage limits are message-rate based (not dollar-based)\n- Only Anthropic's console/claude.ai shows it\n\nLet me open the right page for you:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01GvfwMxiTbGKiU99NbG4z7Q","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"open \"https://claude.ai/settings/billing\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":323,"cacheRead":34217,"cacheWrite":471,"totalTokens":35012,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.004845,"cacheRead":0.0102651,"cacheWrite":0.00176625,"total":0.01687935}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772991275223}}
